类 CustomCategory

  • public class CustomCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    用户自定义分类
    作者:
    zhanghan CREATE TABLE CustomCategory( idCustom INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, customName CHAR(32) NOT NULL, username VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL, isopen ENUM('0','1') DEFAULT '0',//来访者是否可见，0表示所有人，1表示仅自己，默认为0 CONSTRAINT PK_CustomCategory PRIMARY KEY(idCustom), CONSTRAINT FK_CustomCategory_username FOREIGN KEY (username) REFERENCES Account(username) );
